Reference: http://www.gamedev.net/blog/950/entry-2249317-a-guide-to-getting-started-with-boostasio/?st=20&pg=1
Posted by: Drew_Benton

==To Compile==
make 7c
./7b
./7b > 7b.out

==astyle==
astyle --style=allman -U -H -p -f -s4 *.cpp *.h

==To highlight code for html==
highlight -d html -l -t4 -sedit-msvs2008  *.cpp
highlight -d html -l -t4 -Stxt -sedit-msvs2008 *.out

==To update the code to use C++11 features==
sed -i -e 's/boost::bind/std::bind/' *.cpp
there seems to be a problem with std::bind, boost::bind however works


